content: उत्क्रांत {%<ab>p. p.</ab>%} {@--1@} Gone forth or out, departed; उत्क्रांतमिवासुभिः <ls>K. 33</ls>; <ls>R. 7. 53.</ls> {@--2@} Faded, effaced (as colour); <ls>R. 16. 17.</ls> {@--3@} Gone over or beyond, passed, surpassed. {@--4@} Dead. {@--5@} Trespassing, exceeding, surpassing (actively used).
